ch.uzh.agglorecommender.clusterer.treesearch

Class ClusterSetIndexed<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.uzh.agglorecommender.clusterer.treesearch.ClusterSetIndexed<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of object to store in the cluster set.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IClusterSet<E>, IClusterSetIndexed<E>, java.io.Serializable

    public class ClusterSetIndexed<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IClusterSetIndexed<E>
    This cluster set manages the elements to cluster by keeping indices to the elements. For all dual combinations of indices a combination id is created. The set of all combination id's can be used as search space for the best cluster merge.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
